{"tid":1394465,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"梁美芬：支持訂立辱警罪","createTime":"2019-08-01T12:02:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-01T12:33:40.000Z","uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":46,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"165d64f7f2d0ae2517095302e2996d60ef5a4ebc","tid":1394465,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T12:02:58.000Z","msg":"近期有網民「回帶」，找回我2015年支持訂立辱警罪的發言。四年過去，警察執法時面對的侮辱、挑釁有增無減，大家這一個多月以來有目共睹，但辱警罪立法依然毫無進展。所以此時此刻，確實是重溫我的發言的好時間。<br />\n<br />\n全世界好多地方一早制訂了辱警罪，日前紐約有巡警被人潑水侮辱，警方火速拉人，紐約市長嚴厲譴責潑水狂徒「侮辱警察等如侮辱全市居民」 。特區政府要盡快推動立法，保障警隊能在有尊嚴的環境下執法。<br />\n<br />\n一些別有用心的Facebook專頁可能心目中認為中學畢業就是學歷低，曲解了我的發言，我從來沒有認為中學畢業就等如學歷低 、易失控。事實上香港好多中學畢業的人透過獅子山下精神拼搏都好有成就。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/Leungmeifun/videos/682687408869625/?eid=ARD6Ahk8tEEx560uZ-_0PTMaSm806N18E5lyRAyNoeDPzenaxh7_DVAk-YPeL-bYgO6D38xI157jnqlP\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FLeungmeifun%2Fvideos%2F682687408869625%2F%3Feid%3DARD6Ahk8tEEx560uZ-_0PTMaSm806N18E5lyRAyNoeDPzenaxh7_DVAk-YPeL-bYgO6D38xI157jnqlP&d=BmTzKXBjX6ru83xd6aIIEaZPNspveiVXvfzVSLwjqls%3D&h=13743239\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/Leungmeifun/videos/682687408869625/?eid=ARD6Ahk8tEEx560uZ-_0PTMaSm806N18E5lyRAyNoeDPzenaxh7_DVAk-YPeL-bYgO6D38xI157jnqlP</a><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"31d7afe90cbc65e7314440142c6f34c66a7faef2","tid":1394465,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":10,"score":-10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T12:04:15.000Z","msg":"題外話 佢呢幅圖P咗幾耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8WZ4CQP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8WZ4CQP.jpg&h=b2b54fd0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"810616f8207988312c2dd3f580e065067